comments: Butler (MIA) moves along Curry's (GSW) path and makes marginal contact to his body during his driving shot attempt.
Curry (GSW) brushes Adebayo's (MIA) arm and does not affect his shot attempt at the basket.
Robinson (MIA) absorbs the contact to Curry's (GSW) body on-ball.
Robinson (MIA) makes marginal contact to Bazemore's (GSW) body during his shooting motion on the driving shot attempt.
Paschall (GSW) maintains a legal guarding position during the driving shot attempt by Adebayo (MIA) and the body contact is incidental.
Bazemore (GSW) slightly extends his elbow outwards during his driving shot attempt and marginal contact occurs with Nunn (MIA).
Adebayo (MIA) makes incidental contact to Oubre Jr.'s (GSW) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Paschall (GSW) positions his leg in Nunn's (MIA) path but Nunn moves through the marginal contact during his drive to the basket.
Herro (MIA) gathers the ball and takes three steps before releasing his jump shot.
Adebayo (MIA) cleanly blocks Bazemore (GSW) during his driving shot attempt.
Herro (MIA) jumps from A to B into Wiggins' (GSW) body and initiates contact that affects his shot attempt near the rim.
Adebayo (MIA) places his off-arm against Paschall (GSW) at the end of his drive, but releases from contact and does not extend into him.
Bazemore (GSW) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Nunn (MIA) and absorbs the contact.
Robinson (MIA) is in a legal guarding position and the contact is incidental as Curry (GSW) attempts to split the defenders.
Adebayo (MIA) maintains verticality at the end of Curry's (GSW) drive and absorbs the contact.
Butler (MIA) makes incidental contact to Wiggins' (GSW) arm after the release of his jump shot attempt.
Nunn (MIA) and Curry (GSW) make incidental foot contact during the inbound.
Olynyk (MIA) does not release the throw-in within five seconds.
Iguodala (MIA) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Iguodala (MIA) commits a take foul on Curry (GSW).
Curry (GSW) cleanly deflects the ball from Robinson (MIA) during his pass attempt.
